LibreBookmarkSync

This project is an independent open-source browser extension based on the
publicly available Apache-2.0 licensed BookmarkHub source code.

Original project:
  BookmarkHub
  Copyright and authorship retained by the original contributors.
  Project link: https://github.com/dudor/BookmarkHub

LibreBookmarkSync does not include, copy, decompile, bypass, or redistribute
proprietary code from any later commercial or store-distributed version of
BookmarkHub. All new functionality in this source tree is independently
implemented.

LibreBookmarkSync does not provide paid tiers, account login, subscription
checks, or centralized feature authorization.
